metadata.name: 432 VIRUS
metadata.description: This body of work functions as a membership entry to the SNOWCASH exhibition which expands through time and space. This circle traces the origins and culture of the NFTs and the metaverse. Inspired by the "flickering screen"; a crucial element depicted in the Snow Crash fiction novel by Neal Stephenson, it functions as a hallucinatory drug and a virus in the story. Analogue Video, 2022 Edition of 128 By XXXXX XXXX
